videos.headline: Carrington drills long-range 3 for Baylor
videos.description: NaLyssa Smith finds DiJonai Carrington and she pulls up for a deep 3-pointer to extend Baylor's lead to 27-8.

videos.headline: Ursin scores and-1 tip shot
videos.description: Baylor's Moon Ursin cleans up DiJonai Carrington's miss and draws a foul in the process.

videos.headline: Smith comes in for putback layup for Baylor
videos.description: Baylor center Queen Egbo can't sink the layup, but forward NaLyssa Smith flies in for the putback.
